communications.communication:
To Whom It May Concern:

Pursuant to the California Public Records Act, I hereby request the following records:

Any agreements, concert riders and/or contracts between UCSD and Iann Dior regarding his performance at Sun God Festival 2022.

The requested documents will be made available to the general public, and this request is not being made for commercial purposes.

In the event that there are fees, I would be grateful if you would inform me of the total charges in advance of fulfilling my request. I would prefer the request filled electronically, by e-mail attachment if available or CD-ROM if not.

Thank you in advance for your anticipated cooperation in this matter. I look forward to receiving your response to this request within 10 calendar days, as the statute requires.

Sincerely,

Landon Edwards

title: Request for Your Agency's 2022 Roster & Salary Data (Kent County Sheriff's Office)

communications.subject: Maryland Public Information Act Request: Request for Your Agency's 2022 Roster & Salary Data (Kent County Sheriff's Office)

communications.communication:
An excel document is attached.  The Kent County Sheriff's Office does NOT have internal records that would reflect the amount of overtime that was paid to an individual Deputy.  These records are available through the county finance office.  I was able to give you the all of the other information as requested.  

-Sheriff Hickman
